title: MBMBaM 611: Re-Pumba’d
description:
Sometimes you need to put the bits on hold for a moment to do some inner digging and analyze your dreams. What does a sealion mean to you? No, not THAT. Surely not that. Dream interpretation is subjective, but THAT is definitely not correct. Try harder.

 

Suggested talking points: Dukey Man, A Dream Seal Told Me I’m in Love With You, Amber is the Color of My BBQ, Blood Harmony, Secret Bathroom Gushers, The World of Jurassic

NARAL Pro-Choice America: https://www.prochoiceamerica.org/
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Griffin McElroy, Justin McElroy, Travis McElroy)
